The Beverage Forum - Rodney Sacks










































 





The Beverage Forum 

















April 27-28, 2017 
The Westin Chicago River NorthChicago, IL


LIVE SESSIONS
    


















Rodney SacksChairman & CEO, Monster Beverage Corporation
Rodney C. Sacks – Chairman and Chief Executive Officer of Monster Beverage Corporation, formerly Hansen Natural Corporation, since 1990. Under his stewardship, Monster Beverage Corporation’s sales have grown to in excess of $2.7 billion and today employs more than 2,500 people. 
Mr. Sacks is also a Director of Comair Limited, a publicly traded company that operates scheduled airlines under the British Airways and Kulula names in Southern Africa.
Prior to 1990 Mr. Sacks was a senior partner with Werksmans, one of the largest law firms in South Africa.
 
























