Rodney C. Sacks 
Executive Compensation
As Chairman, CEO and Director at MONSTER BEVERAGE CORP, Rodney C. Sacks  made $12,028,955 in total compensation.  Of this total $700,000 was received as a salary, $560,000 was received as a bonus, $5,280,881 was received in stock options, $5,410,360 was awarded as stock and $77,714 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


